    <briefdescription>
<para>A live connection to a Hive Metastore over Thrift. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Construction goes through <computeroutput>Connect</computeroutput>, which parses the URI, selects the transport and opens it so that configuration errors surface as <computeroutput><ref refid="structiceberg_1_1Error" kindref="compound">iceberg::Error</ref></computeroutput> rather than C++ exceptions. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
